<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shì quán shì jiè de zhǔ 迦南783</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì quán shì jiè de zhǔ, nǐ shì měi gè guó jiā de zhǔ.
 nǐ shì měi gè mín zú měi gè jiā tíng, wǒ men měi gè rén de jiù zhǔ.
 nǐ yòng liǎn guāng zhào wǒ men, wàn guó yǐ dé zhī nǐ de dào lù.
 liè bāng yào chēng zàn nǐ, wàn mín yào chuán yáng nǐ, wàn guó yīn nǐ kuài lè huān hū.
 nǐ shì dú yī zhī wáng, nǐ shì quán shì jiè de zhǔ.
 de de sì jí dōu yào jìng wèi nǐ, nǐ yǒng yuǎn huó zhe.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>783</hymn_number>
</song>